1936;;Ladies in Love;;American;;Edward H. Griffith;;Loretta Young, Janet Gaynor, Don Ameche;;comedy, romance;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ladies_in_Love;;Three young women share the rent for a fashionable apartment in Budapest. Martha insists the other two follow a gypsy superstition when moving into a new place, counting the corners of a room and then making a wish: Susie wishes for a hat shop and to be independent of men, Yoli for a rich husband, and Martha for "the impossible", a good home, a man and children.<br><br>